Established in 1974, King Schools is now the one of the leading courses available in the US to obtain your FAA Private Pilots Licence (PPL).

This comprehensive course is known for its light-hearted, easy to follow style. It comprises an 8 DVD pack.
The main sections covered in the course are:

Aerodynamics
Flight Instruments
Sectional Charts
Airspace & Weather mins
Federal Aviation Regulations
Weather
Flight Operations
Radio Navigation
Communications & Radar Services
Cross Country Planning
Aircraft Performance
Weight & Balance
How to Ace Your Test
